  + [gap] is no general mechanism supplies exactly r independent candidates for analytic rank r

& [Lock_003_IndependenceRank] is a closure lock
  + [status] is open_outside_special_cases
  + [evidence] is nonzero height certifies non-torsion in rank 1 and nondegenerate pairings can certify independence when available
  + [gap] is higher-rank nondegenerate height-pairing evidence is often conjectural or setting-dependent

& [Lock_004_UpperBoundControl] is a closure lock
  + [status] is partial
  + [evidence] is Kolyvagin/Euler-system style control can bound ranks in some settings, especially rank at most one
  + [gap] is no general upper-bound/control mechanism is attached to the higher-rank source-measurement pair

& [Lock_005_RefinedFormulaFit] is a closure lock
  + [status] is partial
  + [evidence] is derived regulators and p-adic leading coefficient frameworks point toward refined formulas
  + [gap] is full refined BSD factors and classical-to-p-adic translation are not closed

& [ChecklistFinding] is the result
  + [dimension_closure_status] is not_closed
