  + [second_open_lock] is source_count outside special settings
  + [third_open_lock] is upper_bound_control for higher rank
  + [meaning_gain] is the project now has a precise gate for when a BSD bridge becomes proof-shaped
  + [proposition_update] is current BSD symbolic bridge is a research scaffold whose next mathematical pressure point is nondegenerate independence evidence for enough candidate sources

& [NextResearchTarget] is the next bounded question
